cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.SI

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning, specifically in the context of word embeddings and bias. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a method for debiasing word embeddings, which falls under the category of machine learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely sub-category. Additionally, the paper uses techniques from artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and cybernetics (cs.CY) to address the problem of bias in NLP. Finally, the paper evaluates its proposed method on standard NLP tasks, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SI).
